Akhil is an example of a social media "guru," a word the dictionary defines as an "influential expert," in a field that's evolving very rapidly. A Green Apple Solutions stalwart and a social media enthusiast he likes to make smart and shiny things.

Akhil has been a specialist to help marketers directly measure their social media efforts, and understand how social networks influence marketing performance. He helps removing the guesswork from digital and replaces it with strategies and experimentation built on solid insight. He has helped many companies execute their digital campaigns based on measurable outcomes in the context of broader, multichannel marketing efforts.

Additionally, he heads the HR division at Green Apple Solutions.

In the past, Akhil has worked with hedge funds and trading desks in the US as a consultant and helped some of the top Indian companies with their digital marketing campaigns.

