<h3>Lakshdeep Rajput</h3>
Lakshdeep has more than 8 years of industry experience across IT Consulting, SaaS Products and Digital Marketing. He is highly skilled in identifying and formulating strategies to drive business success using his immense number crunching capabilities.

In his current role at Green Apple Solutions, Lakshdeep is responsible for driving organization strategy; leading the delivery and innovation hub. He heads the Sales and Marketing function and closely monitors the growth of key accounts. Additionally, he looks after Finance at Green Apple Solutions and plays a pivotal role in scaling the client footprint and forming key alliances.

In the past, Lakshdeep has worked with some of the notable hedge funds and financial institutions in the US and UK for their middle and back office technology requirements.

He can be contacted at lakshdeep@greenapplesolutions.com

<hr />

<h3>Naveen Gupta</h3>
Naveen is a 'Specialist' leading the Technology function at Green Apple Solutions. He has helped various clients develop integrated, interoperable and fully scalable business solutions and web applications that function in a complex, distributed environment with heterogeneous platforms. He has the foresight to create solutions which evolve with business growth, while requiring minimum support.

A thorough professional, Naveen plays a vital role in running the SaaS division of the organisation. He has almost 8 years of IT experience and specialises in system-design and development. His in-depth understanding of business processes and data analytics helps him to deliver customized solutions and applications for various industry verticals.

In the past, Naveen has worked with multi strategy and activist funds as for their technology requirements helping them reduce operational risk and costs.

